name: Allowable current intensity (versión 1)
description:
"Makes our lives and worlds safer and more predictable
These machines protect us, these machines protect us
And keep us in a living death, with no protector
What will you do? We are all the same
What will you try for? I can't stop for you"

GPT3 based on IRAM 2444

This happens when you feed an AI with data on electrical safety and ask it to write poetry.
